Performance Evaluation Models

  • MKTRF = Market Risk Premium
  • SMB = Size Factor
  • HML = Value Factor
  • UMD = Momentum Factor
  • RMW = Profitability Factor
  • CMA = Growth Factor
  • LIQ = Liquidity Factor
